<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Where We Drinkin'</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<style>
    p {
        color: #0C0C0C;
    }
    .btn-primary {
        background-color: #481E14;
        border-color: #0C0C0C;
    }
</style>
<body style="background-color: #0C0C0C;">
    <!--Hero Section-->
    <div class="container col-xl-10 col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center g-lg-5 py-5">
          <div class="col-lg-7 text-center text-lg-start">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold lh-1  mb-3" style="color: #9B3922;">It's Happy Hour Somewhere!</h1>
            <p class="col-lg-10 fs-4" style="color: #9B3922;">You've had a long day and you're craving a nice drink, but have absolutely no clue on where to go.
                Well in my opinion, nothing tastes better than a locally made brew. So let's find the best breweries in your area!</p>
            </p>
          </div>
        <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto col-lg-5">
            <form class="p-4 p-md-5 rounded-3" action="/get-breweries" method="get" style="background-color: #9B3922; border: 1px solid #481E14;">
              <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="cityInput" name="by_city" placeholder="Enter a City Name">
                <label for="city">City</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="stateInput" name="by_state" placeholder="Enter a State Name">
                <label for="state">state</label>
              </div>
              <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                 <input type="text" class="form-control" id="zipInput" name="by_postal" placeholder="Enter a Zip Code">
                 <label for="zip">Zip Code</label>      
               </div>   
              <button class="w-100 btn btn-lg btn-primary" type="submit">Find Local Breweries</button>
              <hr class="my-4">
              <small class="text-body-secondary">Have a great time!</small>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
